ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of DENIS JACOB of Lorraine, Quebec, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Ronald K. Clark.
